title: Eric Bailly set to miss Europa League last 16 first leg tie after being sent off for Manchester United after second yellow – but replays showed it was a soft decision
text:
EFL RED MIST Eric Bailly set to miss Europa League last 16 first leg tie after being sent off for Manchester United after second yellow – but replays showed it was a soft decision 
Ivorian will miss United's Europa League last 16 first leg after being sent off for two yellow cards in three minutes Breaking
